"Hey, I'm Prajwal, the developer behind this app! 😊 I love making lightweight and useful apps like Dockside, a streamlined file shelf designed to keep your files and folders at your fingertips beside the Dock.\n\nDockside doesn't collect or share any of your data. It only uses the internet for a license check, and after that everything stays on your device. 🔒 Your privacy is as important to me as it is to you. If you have any questions or feedback, feel free to reach out — I'd love to hear from you. Thanks for supporting indie development! 🙏" = "Hey, I'm Prajwal, the developer behind this app! 😊 I love making lightweight and useful apps like Dockside, a streamlined file shelf designed to keep your files and folders at your fingertips beside the Dock.\n\nDockside doesn't collect or share any of your data. It only uses the internet for a license check, and after that everything stays on your device. 🔒 Your privacy is as important to me as it is to you. If you have any questions or feedback, feel free to reach out — I'd love to hear from you. Thanks for supporting indie development! 🙏";
