"Dockside is currently hidden because these full-screen apps are active:\n%@\n\nIf you continue, Dockside will add these apps to Dockside's full-screen ignore list. You can always reset this later in Settings." = "Dockside is currently hidden because these full-screen apps are active:\n%@\n\nIf you continue, Dockside will add these apps to Dockside's full-screen ignore list. You can always reset this later in Settings.";
