"Hide Dockside when Dock auto-hides" = "Dockside ausblenden, wenn sich die Dock-Leiste automatisch verbirgt";
"When enabled, Dockside follows the macOS Dock auto-hide state and hides itself too. Turn this off if you want Dockside to stay visible even while the Dock is auto-hiding. You can still use Dockside's own hiding behavior separately." = "Wenn aktiviert, folgt Dockside dem automatischen Ausblenden der macOS-Dock-Leiste und blendet sich ebenfalls aus. Schalte dies aus, wenn Dockside sichtbar bleiben soll, während die Dock-Leiste ausgeblendet ist. Du kannst Docksides eigene Ausblend-Funktion weiterhin separat nutzen.";
"This will hide the Dockside, and its behavior is similar to that of the Dock. It will appear when the mouse is near either the Dock or the Dockside. Dockside can also automatically enter hide mode when an app is in full-screen mode or when the Dock is auto-hiding." = "This will hide the Dockside, and its behavior is similar to that of the Dock. It will appear when the mouse is near either the Dock or the Dockside. Dockside can also automatically enter hide mode when an app is in full-screen mode or when the Dock is auto-hiding.";
